    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Projectile weapons consisting basically of a long narrow tube of wood, cane, reed, or metal, through which small darts or pellets are propelled by means of the user's breath.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
